com.cognifide.slice.mapper.api.processor

Interface FieldProcessor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BooleanFieldProcessor, ChildrenFieldProcessor, DefaultFieldProcessor, EnumFieldProcessor, ListFieldProcessor, SliceReferenceFieldProcessor, SliceResourceFieldProcessor

    @ConsumerType
public interface FieldProcessor
    Defines if a field can be mapped to a specified field and performs actual mapping. Class which implements this interface should be added to list of processors in MapperBuilder.addFieldProcessor(FieldProcessor fieldProcessor)

    • Method Summary
